Program: The Documentary
Title: World Stories - Afghanistan's Dancing Boys
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p009hrwl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Sep 2010
The documentaries in this five part series are made by BBC producers across the organisation's language services - from Pashto and Dari, Sinhala, Uzbek, Spanish American to Persian. World Stories are tales told from a local point of view.